DESCRIPTION:The Columbia Democratic Committee meets on the second Thursday
  of each month at 6:30 pm to discuss upcoming elections\, meet local candi
 dates for office\, plan volunteer actions and get-out-the-vote events\, an
 d more. This is a public meeting open to all local Democrats! Meetings tak
 e place in the Columbia Library Community Room. As you enter the library\,
  go to the left past the front desk and turn right to go down to the basem
 ent. You can also support our efforts by making a donation!
LOCATION:Columbia Public Library\, 24 S 6th St 1599\, Columbia\, PA\, 1751
 2
URL:https://www.mobilize.us/lancastercountydems/event/898958/
X-SOURCE:Lancaster County Dems (Mobilize)
